# SQLiteCrawler TODO List

## üöÄ HIGH PRIORITY - Core Features

### Asset Crawling & Analysis
* **Fetch assets** - crawl js/image/iframe/fonts and other linked assets
* **Caching analysis** - report on caching / assets with no cache / cache busting
* **Performance hints** - evaluate preconnect/preload/prefetch for speed improvements

### Advanced Crawling Features
* **CSV crawl support** - crawl from csv (restricted && seed)
* **Proxy rotation** - allow rotating proxies
* **Header rotation** - enable rotating headers
* **Custom extraction** - CSS Path, XPath, regex data extraction
* **Crawl comparison** - enable comparison between crawls (including staging, URL remapping)

### Authentication & Security
* ‚úÖ **Authenticated crawling** - support basic/digest auth for staging sites
* **Security headers** - CSP, X-CTO, Referrer-Policy, X-Frame-Options
* **HTTPS analysis** - HTTP URLs, mixed content detection
* **HSTS validation** - header validation and security analysis

## üìä MEDIUM PRIORITY - SEO Analysis

### Content Analysis
* **Schema.org extraction** - markdown/json-ld parsing
* **OpenGraph analysis** - social media metadata
* **Pagination detection** - rel=prev/next analysis
* **Title tag analysis** - length, uniqueness, boilerplate detection
* **Meta description analysis** - length, uniqueness, duplicate detection
* **Header structure audit** - H1-H6 hierarchy and optimization
* **Content analysis** - thin content detection, word count
* **Language validation** - html lang vs detected language

### Link & Navigation Analysis
* **Anchor text quality** - generic anchors, empty anchors
* **Broken links detection** - 4xx/5xx internal and external links
* **Nofollow analysis** - page-level vs per-link nofollow
* **Faceted navigation** - parameter explosions, session IDs
* **Breadcrumb detection** - navigation analysis
* **Internal links graph** - crawl depth, hub pages, PageRank calculation

### Technical SEO
* **XML sitemap auditing** - analyze sitemap quality and issues
  - URLs not in sitemap
  - URLs in crawl but not sitemaps
  - Non-indexable URLs in sitemap
* **Canonical analysis** - links to non-canonical versions, broken/redirected canonicals
* **Duplicate content** - identify similar/duplicate pages using content fingerprinting
* **Hreflang audit** - international SEO checks
  - Multiple language declarations
  - Mismatching reciprocity
  - Hreflang vs html lang conflicts
  - Invalid language codes
  - Non-indexable URLs in hreflang
* **Redirect analysis** - track and optimize redirect chains

## üîç LOW PRIORITY - Advanced Analysis

### Performance & Technical
* **TTFB tracking** - total download time analysis
* **HTML weight** - oversized pages detection
* **Resource hints** - preload/prefetch/dns-prefetch analysis
* **Render blockers** - synchronous scripts in head
* **Image optimization** - file sizes, modern formats (WebP/AVIF)
* **Favicon validation** - app icons validation
* **Viewport analysis** - mobile meta tag analysis
* **Tap targets** - link density analysis

### Social & Metadata
* **OpenGraph validation** - title, description, image
* **Twitter Cards** - analysis and validation
* **Social images** - aspect ratio, size, reachability
* **Preview images** - favored preview image analysis

### Structured Data
* **Schema.org detection** - JSON-LD, valid types
* **BreadcrumbList** - validation
* **Product/Review schema** - required fields, ratings
* **Conflicting entities** - multiple entities detection

### Domain & Server Analysis
* **SSL certificate** - validation and security headers
* **DNS analysis** - server response analysis
* **Canonicalization** - camelcase canonicalization
* **Search pages** - internal search pages indexing analysis
* **Archive pages** - tag/category archives duplicate risk
* **Parameter handling** - UTM, session IDs
* **Search blocking** - internal search pages noindex/robots blocking

### Advanced Features
* **Content fingerprinting** - using shingle + MinHash/SimHash
* **Image roles** - role=presentation detection for decorative images
* **Meta robots conflicts** - header vs HTML conflicts
* **Canonical conflicts** - missing, multiple, non-200 canonicals, cross-domain
* **Content type validation** - charset validation
* **OCSP stapling** - validation
* **Soft 404 detection** - error detection and reporting

## üéØ API Integrations (Future)
* **Mobile usability** - check mobile-friendly elements
* **Accessibility audit** - WCAG compliance checks
* **Page speed** - Core Web Vitals and performance metrics
* **Image optimization** - alt text, file sizes, formats
* **JavaScript rendering** - detect JS-dependent content

---

## ‚úÖ COMPLETED FEATURES
* Database normalization (canonicals, robots directives, anchor texts, xpaths, hrefs)
* Link analysis & tracking with full metadata
* Crawl management with pause/resume functionality
* Robots.txt analysis and compliance checking
* Retry functionality with exponential backoff
* Sitemap tracking and statistics
* Code cleanup and optimization
* **Authenticated crawling** - Basic/Digest HTTP authentication support (tested on staging site)